Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我雖然也和他接觸了 但讓他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看BUGBEAR
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.45,0:00:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的戰鬥能力和我同等 甚至超越了我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他沒有覺醒 如果魯莽行動的話也會吃大虧的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且現在我們也不知道他擁有什麼樣的奇異能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 那時你衝上摔跤台是過於興奮了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為過於有趣了 所以就情不自禁了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得把爆裂獸給搬來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在今天內解決掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把他引出來 總會有辦法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magus號事件…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一年前的事嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陣你剛才一直在查什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.78,0:00:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這事件新聞沒有報道出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.39,0:00:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 昨晚我不是用奇異能力幹掉一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的沒事了嗎 晴彥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.41,0:01:17.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}所有的歡笑 所有的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.41,0:01:17.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}笑顔も涙もきっと全て
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:24.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一切都是為了與你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:24.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}君に出会うためだった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:43.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}漱漱而下的淚水 在風中飄散
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:43.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}こぼれ行く涙風が連れて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:51.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}以生疏的動作 無數次伸出手去追求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:51.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}慣れない仕草でその先へ何度も手を伸ばした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:56.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}那個不善於表達而受傷的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:56.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}言葉足らずで傷つけた人よ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:02:02.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}現在已經背負起不可磨滅的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:02:02.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}もう取り消せない過去を背負って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:05.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}踏出了新的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:05.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}踏み出して行くんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:12.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}笑顔も涙もきっと全て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:12.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}所有的歡笑 所有的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:19.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}君に出会うための理由だった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:19.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一切都是為了與你相遇的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:25.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}明日があるたったそれだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:25.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只因為這一個理由 就是明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:31.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}僕ら生きる意味になって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:31.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}那將成為我們生存的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:38.61,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}そしてまた日が照らすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 副司令…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的深夜裡有發生過地震嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒收到過這種情報呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚鬥技場停電的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建築物被籠罩在一股不可思議的震動中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是這就是這次的Designer's Child所擁有的奇異能力？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據這邊的調查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個鬥技場裡好像非法聚集了多名少年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行星齒輪裝置的奇異能力到底有多強力呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說奇異能力的話 隊長 你也是有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初出擊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你直覺地感受到KILL-T-GANG的可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這也是奇異能力的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Livlaster的力量啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲平的Livlaster為什麼叫DC呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是Designer's Child的縮寫吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DC的意思是「夢的守望者」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(690,660)\fs32}Dream Catcher
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢的守望者？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指那個驅趕噩夢的護身符？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了它 我不再做噩夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐還是經常做噩夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 每晚都在做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就算醒來了看到的也是噩夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為那個晴彥的未婚妻 也是我的噩夢之一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟這是老爺的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父親只會將人類當做道具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這麼一個販賣兒童的男人卻正是我父親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說這才是最大的噩夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有資格說這種話吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被我買下的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和我父親是一丘之貉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感謝大小姐你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你給予了我容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是你的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貘 拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以再給我演示下那個魔術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是唯一的一張媽媽的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被爸爸發現後 就被他給撕碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貘？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是魔術
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了…你能做到的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問你 你可以用這個魔術只將紅桃A給復原嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜 我還沒有練到那個水平…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…這其實不是魔術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:07:02.37,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(972,286)\c&HFFFFFF&}貘的{\c&HAAEF73&}城市
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不簡單啊 哲平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算打中不會動的靶子也沒什麼可吹噓的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於隊長來說 似乎這點也挺難的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有做過射擊訓練…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你在實戰中倒是像模像樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 隊長…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次用Livlaster來試試？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次看到都會覺得不可思議呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據科學部長所說 與其是你在開Livlaster
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:08:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更像是Livlaster在利用你來開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開槍的你們到底是怎樣的感覺呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒沒有被Livlaster支配的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是種更加自然的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然的感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說 你看著自己的右手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不會有「這是自己的右手」的這種想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手是自己身體的一部分 所以它很自然的就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種感覺不是我和Livlaster兩個個體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且兩者湊在一起才是真正的「自我」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用Livlaster來瞄準目標
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說比起用手槍射擊 更像是扔回力標的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這確實是很棒的奇異能力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我是麗塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華預知到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚Machine Goodfellow將會行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個鬥技場果然很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nebula Engine已經載上彩虹號 在羽田機場待機吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出於戰略上的考慮 我們正在著手把它部署到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 我們只能靠隊長再加把勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們在來一發勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你有點犯規啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 辛苦了 狩屋先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近幾天都是空前的盛況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這都多虧了貘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙可是我們的搖錢樹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚能賺多少就賺多少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚將是他最後一次站在摔跤台上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我會讓別人代替他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的意思…也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就按照您所說的去辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 哲平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去下廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廁所 廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條通道是外人禁止進入的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是冠軍吧…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 面對那種沒有規則的戰鬥 你不感到害怕嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.39,0:11:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不害怕戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所害怕的是 保護不了自己最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 鑼聲響起了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本鬥技場的不敗帝王貘和Great Ramdes的硬碰硬的對決
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一場激烈的戰鬥開始了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AMAROK他們好像不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是我們搞錯了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Great Ramdes一上來就拿出了木刀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是除了遠距離武器外都不算犯規！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然空手接住了對手使出渾身之力揮下的木刀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的強大真是驚人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他有點不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望保護他人的強大嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼遺言嗎 貘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有句話我要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是老子的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那是久美子大小姐的聲音吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貘——！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開大小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要答應我們的條件 我們就當場釋放她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的目的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貘…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動哦 BUGBEAR…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會結束的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們繼續昨晚的未竟之事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經自由了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你做了那種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？那傢伙為什麼還活著？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明被擊中了…但我還活著…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口也幾乎消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在意貘的那個神奇的魔術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還記得Magus號事件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說在橫濱有艘船被炸那件事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是麻野田組的船被炸毀的事件…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得哪裡有蹊蹺了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸發生時幾乎所有的麻野田組的人都在船上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻沒有任何人犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得這可能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個人的思念讓奇異能力發動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個人的奇異能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我對這個只會對我花言巧語的世界感到絕望了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少出去打個招呼啊 久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 在你身旁的是炸彈吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在我們家的地下室找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別做傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚 大家都在船上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親販賣兒童的交易 可以用它做一了斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我每天做的夢才是真實的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你讓我復活的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 貘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:17:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 貘…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我從這個噩夢中解放出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.95,0:17:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼機關？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magus號爆炸的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻野田組的人 其實都死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓大小姐復活 貘讓當時被炸死的人都復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是個特別的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要找到能看見真正的光芒的人生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人其實算是BUGBEAR所創造的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管如何 即使是奇異能力也無法復活死去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為他們不是真正的人類所以才會死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經想起來了吧 BUGBEAR！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個星球是一個噩夢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會將其徹底吞噬！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Machine Goodfellow 爆裂獸 啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Abreaction！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MM車檢檢測到反應
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中心點特定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射程序啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.14,0:19:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Engine Ordinary 射出！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 終於開始了 爆裂獸和Earth Engine的一對一決戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 Earth Engine一上來就要使用兇器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 遠程武器可是犯規的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是BUGBEAR…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓住Earth Engine來打
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種戰鬥方式…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是冠軍嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只顧著跑的話 時間就要到了哦 真夏大地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的氣勢雖然很強…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為什麼…我完全感覺不到他的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒有要保護的人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我又把它弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長你沒事已經很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在裡面操縱的Designer's Child 你知道是誰了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該是他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:21:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個他？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是冠軍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個很強的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他確實很難對付…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.37,0:22:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.21,0:22:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得他像是在一心求死…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也許…是BUGBEAR吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.89,0:22:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？很可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰它
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.66,0:22:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拽什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.88,0:22:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.36,0:22:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.53,0:22:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的城市…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.27,0:22:48.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ふわり風は彼方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.27,0:22:48.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}清風徐徐吹向遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.57,0:22:54.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}涙も連れて行ってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.57,0:22:54.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}請把我的眼淚也一起帶走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:23:01.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}星ほどの思い出たちだって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:23:01.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即使是那些堪比繁星的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:05.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}いいことばっかじゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:05.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}也不全是快樂的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:13.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}瞬いて　君と出逢えた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:13.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}那個閃爍的瞬間 我與你相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:20.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}ねぇ　こんなに近くで遠い今日が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:20.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}今天 這個近在咫尺又如此遙遠的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:31.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}始まる合図はぽつりわたしを呼ぶ声聞こえてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:31.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我聽到了那個開始的信號 在輕輕地呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:40.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}愛してるよりもっと形のない言葉探して行くね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:40.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}要尋找比「我愛你」更加飄渺的情話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:43.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}すぐ側に歩き出して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:43.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我從你身邊走出來
